FlexibleCode is a Field	 	
	
    Representation
    	Group Fields		
 			FieldId 		is Numeric 2
		    Code 			is Alpha 250	
			ExternalValue	is a DynamicField	
			Description		is Alpha 30
			
		
   	Field Rules
		FieldId
			if (Code entered)
				required

			constraint (FieldId >= 0
            and         FieldId <= 25)
				"FieldIdMustBe1Thru25"
		
		ExternalValue
			if (ExternalValue.ValueIs entered)
				Description = ExternalValue.Description
